reviewText: super wonderful very good excellent thank you!
Great! Thanks for all of the great and interesting information !

I am not into Nursing, but planning to do a course on Acupressure. I have seen and experienced effectiveness of Acupressure already. Now I know a few points, usage and also what is to be expected. Practitioners speaking about their experience - all that helped in understanding it as a whole. Its  a wondeful course.. even if you are not a practitioner, but learn this for self care, its a great course to enroll.
Great information and I can't wait to use it in my practice as an integrative nurse!
